<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 03:17:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>韩国峰会制定在军队中使用人工智能的“蓝图”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-summit-target-blueprint-using-ai-military-2024-09-09/</link><description>韩国周一召开了一次国际峰会，寻求制定在军队中负责任地使用人工智能的蓝图，不过预计任何协议都不会具有强制执行的约束力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 02:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-summit-target-blueprint-using-ai-military-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>华兴资本停牌17个月后股价暴跌，前董事长被拘留</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-renaissance-shares-plunge-after-17-month-suspension-former-chairmans-2024-09-09/</link><description>精品投资银行华兴资本的股价周一下跌 72%，创下历史新低，该公司在时任董事长兼首席执行官包凡接受调查期间停牌 17 个月后恢复交易。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 02:11:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-renaissance-shares-plunge-after-17-month-suspension-former-chairmans-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>8月份中国居民消费价格上涨，PPI陷入通货紧缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-faster-pace-august-2024-09-09/</link><description>由于天气原因导致食品成本上涨，中国8月份消费者价格上涨至半年来最快，而随着北京继续努力重振内需，生产者价格通货紧缩加剧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:43:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-faster-pace-august-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国称与菲律宾的关系正处于南海问题的十字路口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-ties-with-philippines-crossroads-over-south-china-sea-2024-09-09/</link><description>在南海紧张局势之际，执政的共产党报纸《人民日报》周一发表评论，中国呼吁菲律宾“认真考虑处于十字路口”的两国关系的未来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:23:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-ties-with-philippines-crossroads-over-south-china-sea-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>美元暂定，日元因美联储降息前景混乱而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-tentative-yen-dips-muddled-fed-rate-cut-outlook-2024-09-09/</link><description>美元周一维持窄幅波动，而日元回吐避险涨幅，因投资者尚未决定美联储本月晚些时候预计的降息规模，并关注本周的美国通胀数据以寻找更多线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-tentative-yen-dips-muddled-fed-rate-cut-outlook-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市下滑，中国通胀出奇疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-09/</link><description>由于对美国经济可能衰退的担忧重挫华尔街，亚洲股市周一下跌，尽管美国股指期货确实从早盘下跌中反弹，债券收益率也从低点回落。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 00:25:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，中国国家主席习近平和俄罗斯总统普京向朝鲜领导人金正恩致以问候</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-russias-putin-send-greetings-north-koreas-kim-jong-un-kcna-says-2024-09-08/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周一称，中国国家主席习近平和俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在朝鲜成立周年之际向朝鲜领导人金正恩致以问候。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 23:16:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-russias-putin-send-greetings-north-koreas-kim-jong-un-kcna-says-2024-09-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国美的集团在香港发行35亿美元股票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-midea-group-launches-nearly-35-billion-share-offering-hong-kong-2024-09-08/</link><description>根据其备案文件，中国家电制造商美的集团周一在香港发行了约 269.7 亿港元（合 34.6 亿美元）的股票，这是该市三年多来最大规模的上市。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 23:07:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-midea-group-launches-nearly-35-billion-share-offering-hong-kong-2024-09-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国计划允许部分地区设立外资独资医院</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-allow-wholly-foreign-owned-hospitals-some-areas-2024-09-08/</link><description>中国周日表示，将允许在包括首都在内的中国九个地区设立外资独资医院，因为北京试图吸引更多外国投资以提振疲软的经济。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 11:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-allow-wholly-foreign-owned-hospitals-some-areas-2024-09-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国对荷兰对ASML芯片制造工具实施新的出口管制表示“不满”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-says-dissatisfied-with-new-dutch-export-controls-asml-chipmaking-tools-2024-09-08/</link><description>中国商务部周日在一份声明中表示，中国对荷兰政府扩大对 ASML 芯片制造设备出口管制的决定“不满意”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 05:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-says-dissatisfied-with-new-dutch-export-controls-asml-chipmaking-tools-2024-09-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国称其巨大市场对美国是机遇而不是威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-says-its-huge-market-is-opportunity-not-threat-us-2024-09-07/</link><description>据中国商务部报道，周六在天津举行贸易谈判时，商务部副部长王受文表示，一个人口众多的现代中国对美国来说是机遇，而不是威胁。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 13:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-says-its-huge-market-is-opportunity-not-threat-us-2024-09-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺提供更多现金，但未能减免非洲债务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-stops-short-africa-debt-relief-pledges-more-cash-2024-09-07/</link><description>中国表示，新资金将用于 30 个基础设施项目，以改善贸易联系，但没有透露细节。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 07:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-stops-short-africa-debt-relief-pledges-more-cash-2024-09-07/</guid></item><item><title>八木在中国和菲律宾造成人员伤亡后在越南造成四人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/super-typhoon-yagi-sets-sight-vietnam-after-tearing-through-chinas-hainan-2024-09-07/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，至少有十几人在海上失踪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 02:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/super-typhoon-yagi-sets-sight-vietnam-after-tearing-through-chinas-hainan-2024-09-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行8月份连续第四个月暂停黄金购买</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-gold-reserves-unchanged-fourth-straight-month-august-2024-09-07/</link><description>周六官方数据显示，中国央行八月份连续第四个月停止购买黄金作为储备。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 02:40:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-gold-reserves-unchanged-fourth-straight-month-august-2024-09-07/</guid></item><item><title>8月中国外汇储备升至2015年以来最高水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-fx-reserves-rise-highest-level-since-2015-august-2024-09-07/</link><description>周六官方数据显示，中国8月份外汇储备升至逾8-1/2年以来的最高水平，这在很大程度上得益于美元普遍走软。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 02:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-fx-reserves-rise-highest-level-since-2015-august-2024-09-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>